{"tid":2505403,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劍指中國｜英國航母下月赴印太首出國 與星馬澳紐聯合軍演","createTime":"2021-04-26T14:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T14:47:54.000Z","uid":239336,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d77d5cad3d5d2c75d692d01ccee3318dae6a6b86","tid":2505403,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"英國國防部周一宣佈，航空母艦「伊利沙伯女皇號」（HMS Queen Elizabeth）將在5月執行首次任務，訪問日本、南韓、印度、新加坡等印太地區多個國家，整個任務為期約半年。國防大臣華禮仕（Ben Wallace）表示，「伊利沙伯女皇號」的部署目標是展示英國在全球擔當積極角色，《獨立報》更形容英國是聯同其他國家，向中國的擴張主義方針表態。<br />\n<br />\n今次是「伊利沙伯女皇號」第一次出國任務，整個行程為期28周，預定到訪40多個國家，並會進行多項聯合軍演，包括與日本海上自衞隊演習，並會跟馬來西亞、新加坡、澳洲和新西蘭海軍舉行聯合演習，紀念5國簽署《五國聯防協議》50周年。<br />\n國防部形容整項任務反映英國側重印太地區，有助英國加強與區內交流，促進該區繁榮穩定。至於「伊利沙伯女皇號」的具體路線目前仍有變數，《每日電訊報》指屆時「伊利沙伯女皇號」有可能不經台灣海峽，以免中國不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210426/EIWHCGGGCBGNHL5OOVC34NBBIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210426%2FEIWHCGGGCBGNHL5OOVC34NBBIE%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B64eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=993ab8ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210426%2FEIWHCGGGCBGNHL5OOVC34NBBIE%2F&h=5ab567d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210426/EIWHCGGGCBGNHL5OOVC34NBBIE/</a>"},{"pid":"13299092f904249a726650045a7a35fa95fe811f","tid":2505403,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"XJP 係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fa885567e2bace8f119ffd9f0796b7de3a34e2","tid":2505403,"uid":309558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXrUSZxv9Pr7J1hsafQBesAVjn88Aif6KMYDRPHixWYo5?filename=rZ2X3YT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZ2X3YT.jpg&h=db5c35b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce50a9a4b72e69